            <h2 id="h2">Here's how it works:</h2>
            <p class="para4"><h4 id="h1">1. Define Your Search:</h4>First Decide who you're looking for. If it's a family member, head to the family category. If it's a friend, the friend category is where you want to be.</p>
            <p class="para4"><h4 id="h1">2. Search by Name:</h4>Enter the full name of the person you're searching for in the search bar.</p>
            <p class="para4"><h4 id="h1">3. Compare Information:</h4>If the individual exists in our database, Finder will retrieve full profile to compare other information.</p>
            <p class="para4"><h4 id="h1">4. Create a Profile:</h4>If the full name isn't found, don't worry. Our platform allows you to create profiles for yourself and your loved ones. fill the details in the below button.</p>
            <p class="para4"><h4 id="h1">5.Stay Updated:</h4>Once your profile is set up, you'll receive real-time notifications whenever there's a new match. You can also visit the site at any time to check if the person is exist or not.</p>
